OL,3,CDonkey stuck up to its belly in mud
OL,4,Cduring heatwave rescued by fire service
OL,6,FA donkey stuck up to its belly in mud
OL,7,Fduring this week's record breaking
OL,8,Fheatwave has been rescued by
OL,9,Ffirefighters in Hampshire.
OL,11,FThe alarm was raised after the animal,
OL,12,Fnamed chocolate, became trapped near
OL,13,FLiss.
OL,15,FA crew from Petersfield were
OL,16,Fdispatched to free her alongside
OL,17,Fanimal rescued trained colleagues from
OL,18,FLyndhurst and Winchester.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
