OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782661674
OL,3,CDonkey stuck up to its belly in mud
OL,4,Cduring heatwave rescued by fire service
OL,6,FThe 20-year-old donkey was dug out of
OL,7,Fher predicament shortly after they
OL,8,Farrived and checked over by a local
OL,9,Fvet.
OL,11,FShe was then escorted back to an
OL,12,Fenclosure and reunited with her herd.
OL,14,FThe fire service, in a statement,
OL,15,Fjoked that the callout had been a
OL,16,F"useful reminder not to leave
OL,17,Fchocolate out in the sun!".
